The paper discusses the design of hardware configurations for Big Data applications, specifically focusing on Cloud deployed clusters. This falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) and Database (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper discusses optimization and prediction techniques, which could fall under Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE), Networked Systems (cs.NE), and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
